@startuml activity_plan_import_allocation
title Activity Diagram - PlanImportAllocation

start
:International Ordering Department triggers allocation planning;
:System loops through each requested merchandise independently;
:Retrieve candidate sites and their in-stock quantities;
:Filter out sites that cannot meet desired delivery date;
:Rank remaining sites:
1. Ship transport over Air
2. Larger in-stock quantity
3. Minimize number of selected sites;
if (Total stock from feasible sites >= requested quantity?) then (yes)
  :Split requested quantity across ranked sites;
  :Generate allocation plan lines;
  :Display draft allocation plan;
  :Confirm and save allocation plan;
  stop
else (no)
  :Generate Insufficient Supply Error;
  :Display error message to user;
  stop
endif
@enduml
